            <div className="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
              <div className="bg-blue-500/10 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-blue-500/20">
                <p className="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-300 leading-relaxed uppercase tracking-tighter">
                  Studio Tip:
                </p>
                <p className="text-[10px] text-white/40 mt-1">
                  Adjust saturation to 110% for vibrant skin tones on passport stock.
